channel.title: Anyone want to be on a succuesful development team?
channel.description:
Was actually just wondering if anyone would like to be on a succesful development team I have 3 years + experience I code everyday frequently some are snippets some are my own codes. I have a 2006 project with 1.5 years of work no one has seen it yet going to release when I feel it is time to release. Other then that hope to find someone soon. Wish you all luck as well.
Thanks, Demolition Owner of 4 days of www.diversityx.tk just released under a week ago!
